&lt;li&gt;Thrives in a high-volume, performance-driven environment, managing a consistent queue of inbound/outbound communications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to efficiently manage a high volume of customer interactions daily while meeting established key performance indicators (KPIs).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
