&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve on finance project teams as requested&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continue to improve processes related to regular activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain all relevant controls related to job duties&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform other duties as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
