&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 3 - 5 years of accounting/finance experience required with an emphasis in investment accounting or NAIC Statutory Accounting. Knowledge of accounting principles and practices and the ability to apply these to job duties.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred:&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
